{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.080", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.600", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Fund von multiresistenten Keimen in Fl\u00fcssen und Seen ist besorgnis\u00aderregend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.600", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.360", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der \u00fcberm\u00e4\u00dfige und unsachgem\u00e4\u00dfe Gebrauch von Antibiotika die Entstehung von multiresistenten Keimen f\u00f6rdert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.400", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Deutschland werden Antibiotika haupts\u00e4chlich in der Human- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Tiermedizin eingesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.440", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber die Ausscheidungen von Mensch und Tier gelangen Medikamentenr\u00fcckst\u00e4nde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.920", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Antibiotika und nat\u00fcrlich auch resistente Keime in die Gew\u00e4sser."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.840", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Sommer baden wir in diesen Gew\u00e4ssern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.360", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und aus einigen dieser Gew\u00e4sser gewinnen wir auch unser Trinkwasser. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verst\u00e4ndlicherweise sind die Menschen besorgt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drei Fragen stehen f\u00fcr mich im Vordergrund: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.120", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.880", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo treten diese Probleme \u00fcberhaupt auf? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.320", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die L\u00e4nder sind daf\u00fcr verantwortlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.240", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Untersuchungen der Oberfl\u00e4chengew\u00e4sser verst\u00e4rkt vorzunehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.040", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen ihre Untersuchungsprogramme erweitern und diese Keime in ihren Untersuchungsumfang aufnehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.000", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.800", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie gelangen die multiresistenten Keime \u00fcberhaupt in die Gew\u00e4sser? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir vermuten momentan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Keime \u00fcber Kl\u00e4ranlagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abschl\u00e4ge von Regen\u00fcberlaufbecken oder auch diffuse Ausschwemmungen in der Landwirtschaft in die B\u00f6den und Fl\u00fcsse gelangen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.120", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bisher ist allerdings mithilfe von wissenschaftlichen Untersuchungen herausgefunden worden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Kontaminationen insbesondere im Umfeld von Krankenh\u00e4usern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber zum Beispiel auch im Abwasser von Flugzeugen zu finden sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.680", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben hier noch deutlichen Informationsbedarf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.160", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist vielleicht der wichtigste Punkt\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie gef\u00e4hrlich sind diese Kontaminationen \u00fcberhaupt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.720", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Tatsache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man in der Umwelt etwas findet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sagt noch nichts dar\u00fcber aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.880", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es wirklich gef\u00e4hrlich ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Analyseverfahren haben sich in den letzten Jahren deutlich verbessert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir brauchen jetzt die Beurteilung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da haben wir momentan einen gro\u00dfen Nachholbedarf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.000", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch in der wissenschaftlichen Forschung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.760", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Klar ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen mehr Informationen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin zuversichtlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.680", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Forschungsprojekte wie das vom BMBF gef\u00f6rderte Verbundprojekt HyReKA schon in n\u00e4herer Zeit neue Informationen bringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einiges liegt schon vor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.600", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Derzeit finden die Abwassertage in Essen statt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.920", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dort wird dar\u00fcber berichtet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen die Wirkung der f\u00fcr uns alle lebenswichtigen Antibiotika erhalten und die Entstehung der multiresistenten Keime so weit wie m\u00f6glich verhindern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.480", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist in erster Linie ein medizinisches Thema. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Verbreitung in der Umwelt zu stoppen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist ein Thema des Umweltschutzes. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb m\u00fcssen wir mit unseren Anstrengungen schon sehr fr\u00fch an allen Stufen des Lebenszyklus eines Medikaments ansetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.840", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "angefangen bei der Herstellung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt bereits Forschungen zu Wirkstoffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich im K\u00f6rper abbauen und gar nicht erst in die Umwelt gelangen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.320", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ansetzen m\u00fcssen wir aber auch bei der Nutzung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen den Einsatz von Antibiotika in der Human- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.400", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Tiermedizin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.640", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "soweit vertretbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.560", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "reduzieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.640", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das m\u00fcssen wir immer wieder hinterfragen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.360", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schlie\u00dflich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.520", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich komme zu einem meiner Lieblingsthemen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.800", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir auch bei der Entsorgung von Antibiotika ansetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.240", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen bundesweit immer wieder darauf hinweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Medikamentenreste richtig entsorgt werden m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.200", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dies m\u00f6glichst mit einer bundeseinheitlichen Regelung verbinden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage es noch einmal ganz deutlich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.680", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kollegin hat es gerade gesagt\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.280", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Medikamente geh\u00f6ren auf keinen Fall in die Toilette! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist absolut richtig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch technische L\u00f6sungen werden in Zukunft notwendig sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das gilt nicht nur f\u00fcr multiresistente Keime; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.680", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch andere Spurenstoffe sind in den Kl\u00e4ranlagen vorhanden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.600", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es werden weitere Reinigungsstufen in den Kl\u00e4ranlagen erforderlich sein; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.720", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wir m\u00fcssen auch dar\u00fcber reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie diese dann finanziert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.280", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meiner Ansicht nach m\u00fcssen diese von den Verursachern finanziert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.840", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und hier sehe ich vor allen Dingen die Hersteller und Inverkehrbringer von Arzneimitteln in der Verpflichtung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.400", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wichtig ist bei all unseren Bem\u00fchungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.240", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir unser Wissen \u00fcber die Entstehung und Verbreitung multiresistenter Keime verbessern und damit den Kampf dagegen effektiver f\u00fchren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.720", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin zuversichtlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.840", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir dieses Problem in Zukunft mit den Forschungsergebnissen in den Griff bekommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.520", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "glaube aber auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.800", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir noch weitere Informationen brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.960", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen freue ich mich auf die Diskussion im Ausschuss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.961", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
